✅ Motion Transfer
✅ 8K Video Upscaling
✅ Face Restoration
✅ Deepfake Detection
✅ Real-time Preview
✅ Batch Processing
✅ Professional Watermarking

## 📚 Documentation

See \`SETUP.md\` for detailed installation and usage guide.

## 🔑 Required API Keys

- Replicate: https://replicate.com
- ElevenLabs: https://elevenlabs.io
- Hugging Face: https://huggingface.co
- OpenAI: https://openai.com

## 📦 System Requirements

- Node.js 18+
